<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3891] CacheValue in CachingDirectoryFactory cannot be used outside of solr.core package</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3891</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CacheValue in CachingDirectoryFactory cannot be used outside of solr.core package. When implementing a new DirectoryFactory (outside of core) which is a subclass of CDF it may be necessary to use CacheValue (similar to RamDirectoryFactory).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
