                            <comment id="13463264" author="phunt" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2012 21:56:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch makes CacheValue protected rather than default permission.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13463272" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2012 22:13:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I changed this to a bug - we pretty much intend that you extend CachingDirectoryFactory to make your own, so this is a rather critical oversight for those wishing to impl their own factory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s also a very, very simple change as it just changes visibility from package to protected (and as a result, two variables from package to public).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
